Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.840,00:03:54.600,辉英,,0,0,0,,So what space are we in here?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.840,00:04:05.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,In what space would you need to define u and v for the bilinear form and the linear functional to be well defined?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.420,00:04:09.460,辉英,,0,0,0,,What linear space do we have to be in?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:09.500,00:04:11.720,辉英,,0,0,0,,What functional space does u and v have to be in?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:12.720,00:04:13.720,辉英,,0,0,0,,Each one again.
