Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.240,00:04:14.360,辉英,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.600,00:04:22.440,辉英,,0,0,0,,So u and v also has to be in each one because their respective derivatives has to be square integrable.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:23.320,00:04:34.040,辉英,,0,0,0,,If I have the derivatives to be square integrable, then I can use Cauchy-Schwarz inequality to guarantee that the weak form is going to be finite.
